high_descs: Head to the ladle on the living room table.
Pick up a ladle from the table.
Turn right to reach the cabinet in the middle.
Put the ladle in the cabinet.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left to reach the countertop on the right.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Turn right to reach the cabinet in the middle.
Put the ladle in the cabinet with the other spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put two ladles in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the ladle on the coffee table in front of the sofa.
Pick up the ladle on the coffee table.
Go straight across to the room with the tall cabinets.
Place the ladle in the middle cabinet in the left corner.
Turn left at the door, go across to the microwave, turn to the countertop.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Head back to the tall cabinet.
Place the ladle to the right of the other spoon on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two ladles in the tall cabinet.

high_descs: Go towards the white ladle ahead of you, standing in front of it with the TV to your back.
Pick up the ladle from the table.
Go right and straight into the narrow room ahead, stopping at the cabinets on your left.
Place the ladle into the middle cabinet.
Leave this room the way you came in, then turn left into the countertop area.
Pick up the ladle to the left of the sink.
Return to the room with the cabinets.
Place the ladle into the middle cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two ladles in a cabinet.
